      • appointmentReminderAlert

        public void appointmentReminderAlert()
        appointmentReminderAlert. This sets up appointment reminder alert and will alert the user if they have an appointment within 15 minutes of sign in. It will display a message that they do not have an appointment if they don't have one within 15 minutes of sign in. This uses a Lambda expression to set a filtered list of all the times that meet our conditions.
